OL,3,CMan in court on terror charges after
OL,4,Craid in Hull
OL,6,FA 23-year-old man is due to appear in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with terror offences
OL,8,Fafter a police raid in Hull.
OL,10,FMikka Lee Anderson, of Morpeth Street,
OL,11,Fwas arrested on 26 February as part of
OL,12,Fa pre-planned operation by Counter
OL,13,FTerrorism Policing (CTP) North East
OL,14,Fand Humberside Police.
OL,16,FHe has been charged with preparing
OL,17,Facts of terrorism, possessing articles
OL,18,Ffor a terrorist purpose, two counts of
OL,19,Fpossessing information for committing
OL,20,For preparing an act of terrorism and
OL,21,Fpossessing a blade in a public place.
