OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772813482
OL,3,CMan in court on terror charges after
OL,4,Craid in Hull
OL,6,FIt came after a residential property
OL,7,Fwas searched. A 23-year-old woman who
OL,8,Fwas also arrested has been released
OL,9,Fwithout charge.
OL,11,FAnderson, a white British national,
OL,12,Fwas due appear at Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court, central London, on
OL,14,FThursday.
OL,16,FDet Ch Supt James Dunkerley, the head
OL,17,Fof CTP North East, said: "We
OL,18,Funderstand that the arrests and police
OL,19,Factivity that have taken place may
OL,20,Fhave caused concern in the local
OL,21,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
