OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772813482
OL,3,CMan in court on terror charges after
OL,4,Craid in Hull
OL,6,F"Public safety remains our number one
OL,7,Fpriority at all times."
OL,9,FHe added: "We will continue to work
OL,10,Falongside Humberside Police and our
OL,11,Fpartners to act on any information
OL,12,Fthat indicates a potential threat to
OL,13,Four communities.
OL,15,F"The public's support is vital to our
OL,16,Fmission to keep people safe."
